'''扣带回'''（英文：Cingulate gyrus）是位于[[大脑|大脑]]内侧的一个解剖结构<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Cingulate Gyrus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/psychology/cingulate-gyrus|accessdate=2021-04-05|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref>。扣带回内部包含大量[[神经纤维|神经纤维]]，其[[灰质|灰质]]皮层称为[[扣带皮层|扣带皮层]]<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Neuroanatomy, Cingulate Cortex|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK537077/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=30725762|first=Fareed R.|last=Jumah|first2=Rimal H.|last2=Dossani|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210221509/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK537077/}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Cingulate gyrus {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/cingulate-gyrus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-05|last=Maingard|first=Julian|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210919030959/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/cingulate-gyrus?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。扣带回将[[胼胝体|胼胝体]]不完全地包裹；在上方，扣带回为[[扣带沟|扣带沟]]所限。

扣带回是脑的[[边缘系统|边缘系统]]/[[边缘叶|边缘叶]]的一部分，其功能牵涉[[情感|情感]]、[[学习|学习]]和[[记忆|记忆]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />。

扣带回接受来自[[丘脑|丘脑]]前核、[[新皮质|新皮层]]的投射，同时也接受来自脑的[[體感系統|体感系统]]的输入。扣带回通过扣带输出到[[内嗅皮层|内嗅皮层]]。

